Commment: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是轉學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是位漂亮的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來有人忘了盯著別人看是很失禮的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎士君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安  騎士君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:22.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（學院內某方面較活躍的學生會被周圍冠以「君」等稱號）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓你受到驚擾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經參觀完學校了嗎？妃宮千早同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  為什麼你會知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梶浦老師告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是3年級C班的七七原薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是同一個班  還有宿舍也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七原同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我薰子就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  我帶你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:03:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一般都不會稱呼學校為「聖應女學院」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是直接說「我們這」或者「聖應」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟其它學校不大一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  我還不夠瞭解這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼說的  形容跟周圍啊社會脫節了的那話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超然脫俗」…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  就這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有人說這裡是「溫室」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概好壞兩方面的意思都有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在上課鈴聲響起前就位做好上課的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們忘了嗎  七七原薰子同學  妃宮千早同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  梶浦老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妃宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  能適應嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  你的媽媽也讓我一定要照顧好你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不必客氣有什麼事就來找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家請安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方首先要將俗語和術語挑明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後不要把助詞弄錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都要在8日前將第二章翻譯後提交上來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的課就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:04:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早的父母是外國人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只不過外婆是北歐人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  抱歉  因為你太擅長英語所以我以為…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算不上擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過我不知道除了學習之外還有什麼事可以打發時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人羨慕  作業竟然要翻譯第二章一整章
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不介意的話  我來教你做如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天放學後有時間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  在邀請她約會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織理  喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開我玩笑啦  我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  薰子  作業是要自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織理啊  你這不是聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪薰子你的聲音太歡悅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是神近香織理同學  跟我們一樣是住校生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  是妃宮千早同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轉學的第一天就傳遍整個學院了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年級才轉學來的確是挺稀奇的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還這麼一頭銀髮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織理  不要再逗千早了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子才剛認識就對人家一見傾心  真讓我不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織理真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回宿舍去了吧  我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,細雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常纖細  如霧一般的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正沒多遠  跑回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優雨  快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都濕了啊  會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使…大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  快醒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話身體會受寒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從宿舍叫初音過來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還是直接帶她回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力氣挺大的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她…優雨看起來很輕的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優雨你怎麼能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身體的事你自己最清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕緊暖暖身才行  要不要喝點湯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  總之先回房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  這還真是讓初音姐姐擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優雨今天早上也沒吃早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上也？那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮了  我叫宮藤陽向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是妃宮千早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽向  請問要借用廚房的話需要跟誰申請？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  並不需要許可的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優雨  不吃點東西的話對身體不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身子還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有胃口的話來一起嘗一下甜點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}　Eton Mess{\r}\N是伊頓麥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由英國伊頓公學發祥的甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將草莓  奶油還有烤好的焗蛋泡戳碎攪拌後再品嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要茶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感謝你  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久沒能跟那孩子相處得那麼開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡的事  我只是給你們送甜點過去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優雨竟然要再來一杯  這種事從沒發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  你又犯平時的壞習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子也感冒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦  完全不是那麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是犯了平時的壞習慣被美女迷住了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…香織理！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是覺得千早好厲害啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉眼就能做出甜點等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完美的女性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  已經被迷得無可救藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織理！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來真的是發燒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連初音都這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓薰子這樣的人誇獎  我非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  在聖應有著低年級學生要作為妹妹服侍高年級學生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高年級學生要做為姐姐教育引導低年級學生的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  史將成為千早大人的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家時一直是以侍女的身份服侍您的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊也將一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好準備了  請動身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住校生們都已入浴完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心有其他人會進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的女性…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想頹廢到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你要不要轉去聖應試試？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的話都是些賢淑的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很適合千早相處的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  媽媽  問題不是這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託梶浦緋紗子小姐就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她是學院長代理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早這麼可愛一定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  不是這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是女學院  而我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史…史？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來給您擦背了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交給史吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:12:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史的使命是用盡一切力量  讓千早大人能平穩度過學院生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是史是女孩子啊  這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連史這種程度的身體都讓您受驚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此以後要在聖應生活是非常困難的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須讓千早大人適應女性身體才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為以觸覺刺激也是非常重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部  胸部壓著我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史  你用不著做到這種地步啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:29.57,title0,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}身為少女的日子與危機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梔子花的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭  這並不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  快離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓其他人看見你在流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們看起來美麗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連招呼也不打一下嗎  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以去證實流言是真實的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能  我並沒有這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你跟其他人略有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  我自己也夠與眾不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織理…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他人怎麼說  我都會誠實地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你問香織理？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個怎樣的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說  我挺喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然毒舌和喜歡捉弄人這點讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她卻是個大好人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是同感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想香織理會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道千早能認真去瞭解她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她有著不少流言蜚語
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來  千早既漂亮又能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一顆為人著想的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你過獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子才是直率而容易相處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  繼續複習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善良…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  想家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織理…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得肯定沒那麼容易矇混過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這就投降了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要公佈於眾我也無話可說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如香織理你想那麼做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是放得開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我有點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是父母之命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然還真能接受這種荒唐的要求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  我家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到泡紅茶我是比不上小史
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以給你泡了花草茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是薄紅葵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅好看  還可以暖和身體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會察覺到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次碰到你時  你顯得十分警戒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你很輕鬆就抱起了優雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管優雨多麼輕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子也不可能輕易地抱起一個女孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在女生看來你完美得甚至讓人妒忌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你飾演著男人眼中最完美的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想就說得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  還有一些只有我才發覺到的細節
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也對我說過  「怎麼可能」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算說出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還希望你能繼續留在這所學院裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我想偷看過我跟她之間的秘密的你會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有自己的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打擾你們的談話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  你方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妃宮千早  今年新住進宿舍的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫凱莉·格蘭塞里烏斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身處黑夜  掌管眾多星辰的星星公主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金星與冥王星交織出的光譜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出你背負著奇異的命運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱莉  過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關門時間快到了  請準備離開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我別人能不能看出你是男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是奉承  我實話實說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你是一個完美的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看穿是因為我是特例
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要說千早你有什麼要改正之處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要注意不要表現得過分完美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  為什麼這麼問？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…只是有點擔心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  史
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  千早大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我始終還是不能融入這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  跟我來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我贏了  千早就要向我坦白一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先取得有效擊中的人勝出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間分出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我贏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就隨你便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}En garde{\r}\N各就位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}Prêts{\r}\N準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我先確認一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時的我  想必顯得十分滑稽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:19:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什麼  你想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早你究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也許你無法相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我除此別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而事到如今  我會離開這裡  離開聖應
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這樣就能解決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是以這種被搖擺不定的心意欺騙著我的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白  所以我要用我的辦法試探你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}Allez{\r}\N開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這點水準嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這種搖擺不定的心意欺騙我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連累了香織理  究竟想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}Halte{\r}\N勝負已分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰子  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是覺得不可饒恕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我也稍微冷靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香織理倒是為什麼放他一馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是偽裝印象戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替千早保守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為代價讓他成為我在學院裡的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼薰子要對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你現在離開優雨她們一定會傷心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…我也挺崇拜你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外你又跟我的姐姐有點相似
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點讓我覺得有點生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我希望你繼續留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早大人  請擦眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭什麼  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是喜極而泣吧  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來一年可以隨心所欲地看女生換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.73,0:22:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是出人意外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾天這麼快就被兩個人發現了真相
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還能繼續留在學院裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史都隱約覺得這是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.87,0:22:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前體育課換衣服的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:22:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿內衣的樣子！
